---
title: Beef Ragu with Spaghetti and Balsamic Mustard Dressed Salad
description: Traditionally, us Brits love the addition of a bit of Worcester sauce in our hotpots, pasta sauces and so on. Here at the Fresh Farm we’re very taken with the idea of using soy sauce in a similar way. The savoury saltiness is a subtle but genius addition to this quick ragu. Can anyone guess your secret ingredient?
